title: ELEMENT 'CLIP #2' NYJAH HUSTON TEASER - SKATEBOARDING
description:
For the second clip leading up to his video, Nyjah Huston doubles down with a two-trick line.

In anticipation of the Nyjah Huston video, we are releasing a new clip, once a week until the video drops, so check back for more footage and information.
